    <h1 style="text-align:center;">TipTop</h1>
   <h3 id="aboutus">At TipTop, we strive to combat COVID-19 issues that businesses are facing. 
     The TipTop app efficiently supports businesses by allowing customers to find and donate to stores easily.
     This app allows users to find small, local businesses through the search engine and can opt for a 
     weekly/monthly/yearly donation rate. A customizable percentage of the customer’s earnings will be donated. 
    </h3>
    <h2>
      Here's the process of the app:
