    <div id="section3">
      <h1 id="how">
        What you can do to help local businesses? 
      </h1>
      <h3 id="source1">
        1. Shop at their stores. The TipTop app allows customers to search for their required items and nearby small businesses. 
      </h3>
      <h3 id="source2">
        2. Donate. Many businesses have been greatly struggling to survive during this pandemic. If you shop at this store often or just want to contribute to the community in any way, 
        please opt to our donation page on our app. Users can manually donate to these businesses 
        or choose the monthly or yearly, automatic payment method.   
      </h3>
    
            
       
